# Fortune AI Agent Service

TypeScript service using Vercel AI SDK for LLM orchestration.

## Setup

```bash
cd agent_service
npm install
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your API keys
```

## Development

```bash
npm run dev
```

## Build

```bash
npm run build
npm start
```

## API Endpoints

### Health Check
```
GET /health
```

### Chat
```
POST /api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "你好"}
  ],
  "stream": false
}
```

## Architecture

```
src/
├── index.ts           # Express server entry point
├── config/
│   └── models.ts      # LLM model configuration
├── agents/
│   └── coach.ts       # Coach agent implementation
└── tools/
    └── fastapi-client.ts  # FastAPI Tool API client
```
